fstests-utils html [branch...]

Generate static HTML dashboards from the JSON digests in
~/fstests-results/<branch>/.  Output under ~/fstests-results/html/.

Pages produced:
  index.html                          branch picker
  <branch>/index.html                 latest run + breakages-in-last-N
  <branch>/tests/<group>/<num>.html   per-test verdict timeline

If no branches given, all branches with a history.json are rendered.

Env:
  HTML_RSYNC_TARGET   rsync target to push the html dir to, e.g.
                      s1:/usr/local/share/site/static/fstests/
